{"tid":2123242,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"自動沖廁馬桶唔好咁大力好唔好 啲水沖到條撚呀","createTime":"2020-07-24T13:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T16:35:31.000Z","uid":77164,"like":36,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5afe25b541bf1542c797af871c8fabded877b8","tid":2123242,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"大家好 又係我 今次又係醫院馬桶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8aAnKrE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8aAnKrE.png&h=13df78b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次陪屋企人睇醫生 香港睇公立醫院要等好正常啦<br />\n咁我等個陣急屎要去廁所<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1zjME0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1zjME0.png&h=aaace3d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oaV4rG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oaV4rG.png&h=8890238a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張嘅角度係由馬桶入面向上望 肉色係我條撚啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRNUAyn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRNUAyn.png&h=27bdd55f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一邊去大梗係一邊玩手機啦 咁有時向前烏下身<br />\n跟住個感應器就瀨野啦<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ib7YhMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fib7YhMJ.png&h=52f5e161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說時遲 那時快 水已經沖左<br />\n咁無乜嘅 咪又係坐低 最多有少少水花<br />\n點知我feel到條撚濕左 屌 啲廁所水太大力 沖到我條撚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqjDhMK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqjDhMK.png&h=fbf2bd71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我即刻彈係身 可惜已經於事無補<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ybRCML.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ybRCML.png&h=022cb2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後即刻攞張廁紙抹條撚<br />\n去大嘅心情已經俾呢次意外搞到所剩無幾"},{"pid":"679995fab4317f12ea6ca6013b8b660bd864154c","tid":2123242,"uid":17426,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"平時屙屎條撚擺係條頸度"},{"pid":"ed00b26ebb6722b8ae6f34fba477b90e9b958e81","tid":2123242,"uid":295230,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"下次合上埋個廁所蓋先再柯，就唔好比水彈到啦，醒目啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e477bc255c6108364a528a8e5da2db7a40400ed","tid":2123242,"uid":2864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲"},{"pid":"571138ca14bb5bd2a5777913a65605d36a8da446","tid":2123242,"uid":231583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b46c274d35743d2e25ffc5da5189559fd5bc090","tid":2123242,"uid":97887,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"真心扔左紙巾先柯<br />\n<br />\n利申：絲"},{"pid":"34893dca57dfe8b57f61bafc0ed8bb2a919d878c","tid":2123242,"uid":77164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"679995fab4317f12ea6ca6013b8b660bd864154c","tid":2123242,"uid":17426,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"平時屙屎條撚擺係條頸度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"甲賀忍蛙？"},{"pid":"6b24de8f688e1a784f40bf451bb252a463611dcd","tid":2123242,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"571138ca14bb5bd2a5777913a65605d36a8da446","tid":2123242,"uid":231583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"今次係廁所水掂龜頭"},{"pid":"2311ca85991d497c557c2b082ff8af580a38c8e5","tid":2123242,"uid":36860,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e37a74e5fe39e115c